---
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>About — The Solo Cruisers</title>
  <meta name="description" content="The Solo Cruisers was built for one reason: solo travelers deserve better than a double-occupancy penalty and a table for one. Meet the team behind the sailings." />
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://thesolocruisers.com/about" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="About — The Solo Cruisers" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Solo travelers deserve better than a double-occupancy penalty and a table for one. Meet the team." />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530103862676-de8c9debad1d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&h=630&q=80" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,400&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Poppins:wght@800&family=Pacifico&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --navy: #173a5e; --ink: #173a5e; --ink-soft: #2a3a52;
      --cream: #faf6ef; --cream-deep: #f1e9dc;
      --brass: #b8893f; --brass-light: #c8a14e;
      --teal: #46bcd0; --teal-light: #7ad4e2;
      --text: #2a2a28; --muted: #6f6f68; --line: #e3dccf;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: var(--text); background: var(--cream); line-height: 1.6; }
    h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.1; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
    .wrap { max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
    .eyebrow { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--brass); margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block; }

    /* NAV */
    .nav { padding: 1.2rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); background: var(--cream); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50; }
    .nav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; }
    .brand-svg { width: 42px; height: 42px; }
    .brand-name { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.8rem; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-soft); transition: color 0.2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--brass); }
    .btn-pill { background: var(--teal); color: #fff !important; padding: 0.55rem 1.3rem; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 600 !important; font-size: 0.85rem !important; transition: background 0.25s; }
    .btn-pill:hover { background: var(--navy) !important; }

    /* HERO BAND */
    .page-hero { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); padding: 6rem 0 5rem; text-align: center; }
    .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .page-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--brass-light); }
    .page-hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.8; }

    /* STORY */
    .story-band { padding: 6rem 0; }
    .story-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: center; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .story-img { border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; height: 480px; }
    .story-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
    .story-text h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .story-text p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }

    /* VALUES */
    .values { background: var(--cream-deep); padding: 6rem 0; }
    .values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 2.5rem; margin-top: 3.5rem; }
    .val-card { background: var(--cream); padding: 2.25rem 2rem; border-radius: 6px; border-top: 3px solid var(--brass); }
    .val-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .val-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; }

    /* STATS */
    .stats { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); padding: 5rem 0; }
    .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .stat-num { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.4rem); color: var(--brass-light); font-weight: 500; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top: 0.4rem; text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-band { padding: 6rem 0; text-align: center; }
    .cta-band h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .cta-band p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .btn-solid { background: var(--teal); color: #fff; padding: 0.95rem 2.4rem; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; display: inline-block; transition: background 0.25s, transform 0.25s; }
    .btn-solid:hover { background: var(--navy); transform: translateY(-2px); }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer { background: var(--ink); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); padding: 3rem 0 2rem; text-align: center; }
    footer p { font-size: 0.82rem; }
    footer a { color: var(--brass-light); }

    @media (max-width: 940px) {
      .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .story-img { height: 320px; }
      .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 2.5rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="nav">
    <div class="wrap nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="brand">
        <div class="brand-svg">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect width="100" height="100" rx="24" fill="#46BCD0"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="46" fill="white"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="34" stroke="white" stroke-width="22"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="34" stroke="#E5443B" stroke-width="22" stroke-dasharray="26.7 26.7" transform="rotate(45 50 50)"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" stroke="#173A5E" stroke-width="3"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="23" stroke="#173A5E" stroke-width="3"/>
            <path d="M41 55 H59 L57 60 Q56 63 53 63 H47 Q44 63 43 60 Z" fill="white" stroke="#173A5E" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <rect x="46" y="49" width="8" height="6" fill="white" stroke="#173A5E" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <rect x="50" y="45" width="4" height="4" fill="#FF7A4D" stroke="#173A5E" stroke-width="1.2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="brand-name">Solo Cruisers</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="/#story">Why Us</a>
        <a href="/#cruises">Cruises</a>
        <a href="/destinations">Destinations</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn-pill">Plan Your Voyage</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--brass-light);">Our Story</span>
      <h1>Built for the solo traveler<br><em>who refuses to stay home.</em></h1>
      <p>We started The Solo Cruisers because we kept hearing the same story: "I'd love to cruise, but not alone." We fixed that.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story-band">
    <div class="wrap story-grid">
      <div class="story-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488646953014-85cb44e25828?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
          alt="Solo traveler looking out over the ocean" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="story-text">
        <span class="eyebrow">Why We Exist</span>
        <h2>The solo supplement was never fair. We fixed it.</h2>
        <p>The cruise industry was built for couples and families. Solo travelers get penalized — charged double for a cabin they're only half-filling. We thought that was wrong, so we built a different model.</p>
        <p>Every sailing we host is designed from the ground up for single adults. No second-person ghost charge. No awkward table assignments. No feeling like an afterthought. Just a great ship, a curated group, and a team that handles every detail before you even pack.</p>
        <p>We've hosted thousands of solo sailors across dozens of sailings. The departures change. The friendships don't.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span class="eyebrow">What We Stand For</span>
      <h2>Three things we never compromise on.</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="val-card">
          <h3>No Solo Penalty</h3>
          <p>We negotiate group rates that eliminate or dramatically reduce the single supplement. You shouldn't pay more for the same cabin just because you're traveling alone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-card">
          <h3>Genuine Community</h3>
          <p>Every sailing is hosted — cocktail mixers, group dinners, shared excursions. You meet your people before you board and stay connected long after you disembark.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-card">
          <h3>Your Independence, Intact</h3>
          <p>Community doesn't mean mandatory. Prefer a solo shore day? A quiet dinner? That's your call. We build the social infrastructure. You decide how much you use it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stats">
    <div class="wrap stats-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">10,000+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Solo sailors hosted</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">200+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Hosted sailings</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">4.9★</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Average traveler rating</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">All Ages</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Welcome aboard</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span class="eyebrow">Ready?</span>
      <h2>Your next adventure is one call away.</h2>
      <p>Tell us where you want to go and we'll match you to the right sailing, handle the logistics, and introduce you to your crew.</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn-solid">Plan Your Voyage →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="wrap">
      <p>© 2026 The Solo Cruisers · <a href="tel:+1-800-000-0000">Contact Us</a> · <a href="/faq">FAQ</a></p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
